t: Amazon Fresh Supermarket One Step Closer to Opening in Northern Liberties - PHILADELPHIA.Today
s: March 20, 2025 - The opening of the Northern Liberties store would be part of Amazon’s plan to double the number of Amazon Fresh grocery stores in the Philadelphia area. Another store is set to open in Bensalem. If and when they are opened, the two new Philly-area stores would join two other stores in Broomall. Amazon, who also owns the Whole Foods Markets grocery chain, said it wasn’t going to expand Amazon Fresh to new locations until it found a better strategy for the brand...
